verbose_text: The genetic variant +3953 (rs1143634) in IL-1beta has been suggested to influence production of IL-1beta protein [XREF_BIBR] while the variable number tandem repeat (VNTR) variant (rs2234663) in anti-inflammatory IL-1 receptor antagonist (IL-1RA, also called IL-1RN) has been proposed to influence expression of IL-1RA protein [XREF_BIBR].
